View.name: cubeview_datecomparison
View.SQLText: REPLACE VIEW DWP01A_APP_EHR_DATETOOL.cubeview_datecomparison AS (SELECT dc.ComparisonID ,dc.Comparison FROM (SELECT 0 (NAMED ComparisonID ),CAST(('Regular') AS VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET UNICODE NOT CASESPECIFIC)(NAMED Comparison )) dc UNION ALL SELECT dc.ComparisonID ,dc.Comparison FROM (SELECT 1 (NAMED ComparisonID ),CAST(('Last Year') AS VARCHAR(50) CHARACTER SET UNICODE NOT CASESPECIFIC)(NAMED Comparison )) dc )
